Subscribe to UIC Today
For email updates




Current UIC students, faculty and staff
All students, faculty and staff are automatically suscribed to UIC Today.







Community members, retirees, alumni and others
Subscribe or unsubscribe with the designated instructions below.


To subscribe to UIC News, send an email with no subject to listserv@uic.edu and type in the message body: subscribe uicnews Your Name


To unsubscribe to UIC News, send an email with no subject to listserv@uic.edu and type in the message body: unsubscribe uicnews Your Name




